02:01.545 --> 02:03.207
And I'd be looking out my bedroom window.

02:03.307 --> 02:04.970
And again, I was very religious.

02:05.010 --> 02:11.359
So I had statues of Jesus in my bedroom, and I would kiss the head of Jesus often.

02:11.780 --> 02:14.524
I didn't know him personally, but God was drawing me to himself.

02:15.205 --> 02:19.291
I would one day confess Jesus as the Lord and Savior of my life at 19.

02:19.651 --> 02:21.554
But before that, very religious.

02:22.306 --> 02:25.330
I remember kissing the head of Jesus for one reason or another.

02:25.390 --> 02:28.073
