02:28.113 --> 02:32.979
And I accidentally hit Jesus and knocked him off the shelf, the windowsill, and his head fell off.

02:33.619 --> 02:35.542
And so his head is on the ground decapitated.

02:35.582 --> 02:36.262
I'm like, what?

02:36.643 --> 02:38.024
Jesus, what did I do to you?

02:38.585 --> 02:41.609
Now this is a young mind trying to figure out the things of God.

02:41.689 --> 02:43.811
And so I put his head back on and I glued it.

02:44.472 --> 02:49.618
And so I went on until one day, Jesus himself, not a statue, but Jesus himself,

02:49.890 --> 02:53.474
would call me to himself and say, I want you to be a follower of mine.

02:54.075 --> 02:56.738
And I was just so excited to go to church all the time.

02:57.558 --> 02:59.300
And I don't wanna ever lose that excitement.

03:00.001 --> 03:07.089
And I pray that as you get into God's word with me, that your excitement would only grow for the love of Christ.

03:07.349 --> 03:09.091
Jesus alone, didn't we just sing that?

03:09.672 --> 03:11.694
Jesus alone, do you love Jesus?

03:12.295 --> 03:13.857
