04:10.555 --> 04:13.459
Verse three, my soul also is greatly troubled.

04:13.880 --> 04:15.602
But you, O Lord, how long?

04:16.002 --> 04:17.484
Have you ever asked the Lord, how long?

04:18.104 --> 04:18.965
