08:26.779 --> 08:28.561
Have you seen the movie Jesus Revolution?

08:29.382 --> 08:30.524
It's a phenomenal movie.

08:30.544 --> 08:31.986
I've seen it I think five times.

08:32.738 --> 08:37.825
I don't watch movies usually that many times, but this is the story of a man that loved Jesus.

08:37.885 --> 08:39.167
He was called into the ministry.

08:39.627 --> 08:44.855
In fact, it wasn't until he was about 40 years old that a hippie named Lonnie Frisbee shows up into his life.

08:45.375 --> 08:50.743
Now, before that, there were many valleys in Chuck Smith's life, many ministries that didn't bear fruit.

08:51.103 --> 08:57.312
