08:59.746 --> 09:03.592
He was going through valleys, but he hung in there and he just wanted to be faithful to Jesus.

09:03.632 --> 09:06.316
And this hippie shows up in 1966.

09:07.398 --> 09:20.438
And if you've seen the movie, if you know some of the history of the Jesus movement or the Calvary Chapel movement, you'll know that from there, thousands upon thousands of people then get born again, churches are planted all around the world.

09:20.458 --> 09:23.282
There's about a thousand or so Calvary chapels around the world.

09:24.770 --> 09:30.297
But you would have never known that if you watched the movie and you're thinking, wow, you know, he did struggle, you know, chapel, Costa Mesa.

09:30.538 --> 09:32.621
But you don't know some of the story before that.

09:34.263 --> 09:36.566
See, I don't know some of the story that you're going through.

09:36.626 --> 09:37.928
Some of you I'm looking at you right now.

09:37.948 --> 09:38.929
