10:02.124 --> 10:05.348
Because they're going to be part of our life as long as we're on this side of heaven.

10:07.030 --> 10:09.293
But how do you exit out of your valley?

10:09.593 --> 10:12.356
I want you to know that it's not temporary, it's only going to be first season.

10:12.697 --> 10:15.020
David said this, though I walk what?

10:15.460 --> 10:18.124
Through the valley of the shadow of death.

10:18.624 --> 10:20.146
You're not supposed to set up camp there.

10:20.834 --> 10:22.556
You're not supposed to permanently live there.

10:22.576 --> 10:25.039
