12:10.621 --> 12:13.906
That's the purpose of some of these valleys that we go through.

12:14.082 --> 12:19.107
But there's something else that I want you to remember, and that is the providences of the Lord.

12:20.548 --> 12:22.150
Now, what are providences?

12:23.531 --> 12:24.432
What are providences?

12:24.852 --> 12:27.875
These are times in your valley where you have seen God show up.

12:28.996 --> 12:30.017
Maybe God glimpses.

12:31.598 --> 12:33.180
Maybe God gives you a revelation.

12:33.740 --> 12:35.622
He says to you, I'm going to take care of you.

12:35.682 --> 12:37.844
