12:38.825 --> 12:44.050
I am coming on your behalf to take care of what needs to be taken care of in your life.

12:45.154 --> 12:51.082
The providences, the verse says, surely goodness in mercy shall follow him.

12:51.102 --> 12:53.185
You could actually change that word surely.

12:53.646 --> 12:57.131
And the more literal rendering of that word would be only.

12:57.171 --> 13:00.355
David says only goodness in mercy.

13:00.375 --> 13:04.861
What confidence he has in the character and the commitment of God towards him.

13:05.362 --> 13:08.366
This is what's going on as he says this word right here.

13:08.667 --> 13:11.110
He says that God sees to my life.

13:12.051 --> 13:13.874
This is literally what he's talking about.

13:14.018 --> 13:15.179
God sees to it.

13:15.940 --> 13:20.124
Now if I went up to you and I said, man, I really need to do something for me and you said something like this.

13:20.364 --> 13:21.165
I'll see to it.

13:22.926 --> 13:30.674
This is Almighty God who's saying to us his providences is that he's saying to you in your valley, I'm going to see to it.

13:32.015 --> 13:32.976
Does that make any sense?

13:33.476 --> 13:43.986
That's a word you're going to need to know in the middle of your valley that God is fully capable and sovereign and loving and he's also providential.

13:45.090 --> 13:53.663
Meaning he's saying to you, I am gonna see to it that every need that you could ever have in the middle of your valley is going to be taken care of.

13:55.085 --> 13:58.450
Remember the providences of the Lord.

13:58.771 --> 14:00.153
This is how you get out of your valley.

14:00.413 --> 14:06.763
You're gonna go back in your mind and you're gonna see God showed up there, God showed up there, God showed up over here.

14:06.783 --> 14:07.664
This is what David does.

14:07.905 --> 14:14.194
That's why he can say with confidence surely or only goodness and mercy, shall follow me all the days of my life.

14:14.818 --> 14:15.740
Are you that confident?

14:16.941 --> 14:18.845
Are you that sure, as David was?

14:20.327 --> 14:22.030
