35:23.070 --> 35:25.394
John Newton wrote to him, does anybody know?

35:26.455 --> 35:27.336
Amazing grace.

35:29.159 --> 35:31.302
So William Cooper understood valleys.

35:33.325 --> 35:39.634
His whole life he never married, got completely slandered.

35:40.386 --> 35:42.008
because of his bachelorhood.

35:42.468 --> 35:48.414
Can you imagine what happens today when people are saying such cruel things about people?

35:48.434 --> 35:50.435
That happened back in those days too.

35:51.356 --> 36:01.846
And he was the recipient of all of that that led him into a life of one valley after another valley until the day that he died.

36:03.148 --> 36:04.809
He writes, he's a poem writer.

36:05.249 --> 36:06.030
He wrote hymns.

36:07.271 --> 36:10.034
Here's one that has meant the world to me

36:10.306 --> 36:13.650
in the middle of the valleys that I have gone through.

36:14.351 --> 36:17.435
It's called God works in mysterious ways.

36:18.356 --> 36:18.756
Are you ready?

36:19.757 --> 36:20.338
He said this.

36:21.820 --> 36:25.965
God moves in mysterious ways, his wonders to perform.

36:26.005 --> 36:31.251
He plants his footsteps in the sea and rides upon the storm.

36:32.833 --> 36:40.082
Deep in unsearchable minds of never failing skill, he treasures up his bright designs

36:40.354 --> 36:42.357
and works his sovereign will.

36:43.659 --> 36:48.125
Judge not the Lord by feeble sense, but trust him for his grace.

36:49.407 --> 36:54.374
Behind a frowning providence, he hides a smiling face.

36:56.256 --> 37:00.122
His purposes will ripen fast, unfolding every hour.

37:00.182 --> 37:05.129
The bud may have a bitter taste, but sweet will be the flower.

37:06.851 --> 37:09.074
Blind unbelief is sure to air,

37:09.474 --> 37:20.811
and scan his work in vain, for God is his own interpreter and he will make it plain in his own time, in his own way.

37:22.573 --> 37:30.244
Father, we pray that you would help us to be the kind of people that realize that you will always provide.

37:30.425 --> 37:36.754
You see ahead and then you meet every single need in the valley and out of the valley.

37:37.762 --> 37:47.557
We will remember your providences, Lord, and we will return to your promises, as William Cooper did, over and over and over again.

37:47.577 --> 37:59.535
I pray, Lord, for my brothers and sisters sitting here, especially those who raised their hand, testifying publicly in front of others that there is a valley they had gone through or are going through.

38:00.877 --> 38:06.546
And so, God, I know that you're speaking to them, that you're going to lead them out of their valley.

38:07.554 --> 38:08.795
And so, Lord, we trust you.

38:09.776 --> 38:10.918
We even sing praises.

38:11.719 --> 38:13.320
We will dance before you, Lord.

38:13.901 --> 38:16.124
You turn our morning into dancing.

38:16.164 --> 38:17.005
This is what you do.

38:18.226 --> 38:19.808
And so, Lord, we just say we love you.

38:20.008 --> 38:23.592
Thank you for speaking your truth to us this morning.

38:24.233 --> 38:35.225
I pray, Lord, for those in depression, specifically, that they would hear a word from you right now, that you're ever present with them, that you're seeing to their life.

38:35.385 --> 38:36.306
You're seeing to it.

38:36.994 --> 38:44.707
To take care of it, may this truth go deep inside of their soul, even now, that you would bring them out.

38:45.548 --> 38:52.940
Remove the clouds of melancholy, as they would say back in the old days, the days of gloom, the dreary days of winter.

38:53.902 --> 38:57.347
I pray God and we pray that it becomes the bright days of summer for them.

38:58.449 --> 39:03.858
In Jesus' mighty name, amen.

39:06.274 --> 39:10.202
Thanks for listening to the Crossway Christian Church's Middleford campus sermon podcast.

39:10.523 --> 39:17.758
If you like to plug into the life of our community or have any questions that we might be able to answer, visit our website at CrosswayCC.org to connect with us.

39:18.219 --> 39:19.502
Until next time, we can be with you.

39:19.783 --> 39:21.426
May the Lord bless you and keep you.

